Tham s n_estimators xc nh s lng cy quyt nh c s dng trong m hnh random forest. Mt gi tr ln ca n_estimators s dn n vic xy dng mt s lng ln cc cy quyt nh v tng chnh xc ca m hnh, nhng ng thi cng lm tng thi gian hun luyn v phc tp ca m hnh. Trong khi , mt gi tr nh ca n_estimators c th lm gim chnh xc ca m hnh

# p dng thut ton Ramdon Forest hin th tnh nng quan trng nh hng n vic phn loi cua
importance = rfc.feature_importances_
features = ['fontallip', 'rearwidth', 'length', 'width','depth']
df = pd.DataFrame({'features': features, 'importance': importance}).sort_values('importance', ascending=False)
print(df)

In [14]:
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

# Tnh ton s lng cc gi tr d on ng v sai
correct = (y_pred == y_test).value_counts()[True]
incorrect = (y_pred == y_test).value_counts()[False]

# Hin th  th  chnh xc
plt.bar(["Correct", "Incorrect"], [correct, incorrect])
plt.title("Accuracy on Test Set: {:.2f}%".format(accuracy*100))
plt.xlabel("Prediction")
plt.ylabel("Count")
plt.show()

Tham s C l mt h s iu chnh quan trng gia vic ti a ho rng ca vng gia cc l v vic ti thiu ha s mt mt ca m hnh. Nu gi tr ca C ln, m hnh s c gng ti a ho rng ca vng gia cc l, ng thi s phi chp nhn mt mt ln hn nu cc im d liu khng c phn loi ng. Nu gi tr ca C nh, m hnh s tp trung vo vic gim thiu mt mt, ng thi s c vng gia cc l nh hn.
